name: Garage Doors Hero
description: Garage Doors Hero is a reputed family owned and operated garage door service company which has been serving the people in Menifee, CA for over 20 years. Whether you need a major garage door repair, a renovation or maintenance, we deliver quality service at a fair service and are passionate about what we do. We provide a full consultation to explain all available options so that you can choose the service that is right for your home. Our services include installation (new garage door, garage door opener, motors, springs, key pads), repair (garage door openers, broken springs, cables/doors off track, damaged panels, remotes/key pads), maintenance (annual door maintenance, safety inspection, lube and tune), lifestyle screen doors (fully retractable, spring loades system that works in conjunction with your existing garage door).
